'''Madison Ellen Lloyd Broadbent''' ([[August 22]], [[1991]] &mdash; [[July 16]], [[2018]])<ref name="Legacy" /> portrayed an [[Unidentified Naboo child|unnamed Naboo child]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']]. She was the younger sister of [[Jake Lloyd]].

On July 16th, 2018, Madison Ellen Lloyd Broadbent passed away of natural causes.<ref name="Legacy" />

